description.content:
PLEASE DISCUSS WITH ME BEFORE PLACE ORDER


Hello there, I hope you are doing good! My name is Sehar. A Senior Web Developer.


Why to choose me?

I have experience of large range projects, including but not limited to a blog, e-commerce, agency, directory listing, job portal, real-estate, and many more. I work with a focus on Standard, Aesthetics, and Professionalism to deliver the right product for your business.


Whats I will Provide


  • 100% Client satisfaction
  • Highly professional and responsive design on all devices
  • All browsers compatible
  • SEO and Mobile friendly structure
  • Speed optimized
  • Elementor, visual composer, Divi Page Builder support
  • Customized design
  • E-commerce with various payment integrations
  • Premium WordPress themes
  • FREE copyrights images and graphics
  • Secured and user-friendly admin panel
  • Social media integration
  • Live chat integration
  • Mailchimp or other mailing lists integrations
  • Content upload
  • EXTRA BONUSES
  • Unlimited Support for My Clients and much more


We Guarantee

  • Fully secured 
  • Fast loading pages for better conversion and navigability
  • Fully responsive
  • Guidance Videos


So, what are you waiting for?


Let's Chat!

Sehar did a fantastic job transforming my website! The final product looks a hundred times better and truly reflects the vision and mission of my brand. The service was quick, efficient, and highly professional, and the quality of work was absolutely top-notch. I couldn’t be happier with the outcome.

If you’re looking for someone who understands your needs and delivers with excellence, I highly recommend Sehar’s services!

Couldn't be happier with Sedar's complete website re-design she performed on my existing website. It looks much more professional and polished. She was easy to work with, very helpful with the steps and patient with guiding me along. Highly recommend.
Fantastic turn around time for updated website and transfer to Wordpress. She guided me along the way, made suggestions that saved me $$ with hosting, etc. wonderful!

I would like to sincerely thank you for the incredible effort and professionalism you put into the creation of our website. 

Throughout our extensive collaboration, with numerous modifications and adjustments, your dedication and expertise were evident at every step.

The final result is truly appreciated, and we are more than satisfied with the outcome.

Your commitment to delivering a high-quality product has truly exceeded our expectations.

Thank you once again for your hard work and exceptional service.
Delivered a website in less time than expected.. and she also did above and beyond what was expected!! Will always use her services!! 👏 👏
